## 🏗 Project Structure

```
WinkartApp/
├── app/
│   ├── _layout.tsx          ← Root + fonts + safe area
│   ├── location.tsx         ← Location selector screen
│   ├── search.tsx           ← Search results (3-col grid)
│   ├── (tabs)/
│   │   ├── _layout.tsx      ← Bottom tab bar (5 tabs)
│   │   ├── index.tsx        ← Home screen
│   │   ├── categories.tsx   ← Expandable categories
│   │   ├── bills.tsx        ← Bill history list
│   │   ├── cart.tsx         ← Cart with qty controls
│   │   └── profile.tsx      ← Profile + settings menu
│   ├── shop/[id].tsx        ← Single shop screen
│   ├── product/[id].tsx     ← Single product screen
│   └── bill/[id].tsx        ← Invoice detail screen
└── constants/Colors.ts      ← Design tokens
```

